reviewText: mistakes on 2 of the tests.  Should have read "Expenses" in question #2, not "Revenue"

Far too many errors in the marked tests, questions referring to the wrong answers, duplicate questions with different correct answers.  For a course on accountancy I would have expected zero errors.  Presentation and delivery by the instructor however was really good.
The information was easy to follow and understand. The number of errors in the quizzes were frustrating, as when the correct answers are selected, the software counts it as incorrect.
excellent training. Professor is super knowledgeable easy to understand steps.
Fantastic!!!! This is by far the best and most educational of all.
A​llah bless you , it was very helpful to me i am vey glad to gane this Certificate , thanks so so much.
The course is well designed and the trainer is really good. It gives a clear picture of an accounting cycle.

The content creator breaks down each cycle down into small, easy to grasp steps. The subsequent quiz and short assignment ensures that you've truly grasped the concept. It is also very easy to go back and re-watch any of the videos while completing the assignment if you need help. Definitely a great way to review these concepts in short, digestible pieces. There are a few errors in the quizzes, but overall great content.

I appreciate this introduction course. I will continue to learn more through other more advance course.
